summary: hey u know what shoutout to everyone who didn't get to see dnp on tour, shoutout to ppl who couldn't make it or whose countries...
body: hey u know what shoutout to everyone who didn’t get to see dnp on tour, shoutout to ppl who couldn’t make it or whose countries or states weren’t even in the tour; shoutout to everybody in this fandom for supporting ii regardless of whether they were going or not; shoutout to all of you who probably felt sad this summer bc of the meet and greet pics and the ig stories and things happening on stage. i just want you to know ur valid and ur not forgotten. interactive introverts isnt just for people who went to see it, it was for all of us and i hope you feel like it when the ii movie goes up.
